<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url("desktop-wallpaper-get-the-latest-movies-data-src-kodi-tv-shows-teahub-io (1).jpg") no-repeat center center/cover;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 150px; 
            height: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-left: 50px;
        }


        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            color: white;
            padding-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            min-height: 70px;
            border-bottom: 1px  ;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            
        }

        header h1 {
            padding: 5px 0;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content{
            width: 670px;
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 20px 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            
        }
        .content p{
            color: white;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #333333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .footer i {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img src="1.PNG" class="logo">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Us </h1>
        </div>

    </header>

    <div class="container content">
        <h2>Welcome to Our Movie Database!</h2>
        <p>
            Our Movie Database offers comprehensive information about movies, TV shows, actors, and filmmakers. We're dedicated to providing our users with accurate and up-to-date information about their favorite films and shows. Whether you're looking for ratings, reviews, or cast information, we've got you covered!
        </p>

        <p>
            Our team is passionate about movies and entertainment, and we strive to maintain a platform where movie fans can come together to share their knowledge and insights. We're constantly updating our database to ensure that you have access to the latest information in the world of cinema.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Contact us</p>
        <p class="help"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> <a href="#">Help & Support</a></p>
    </div>
    <script src="AboutUs.js"></script>
</body>
</html>